title: Jake Wood, Co-Founder Of Team Rubicon
teaser: Host Jessica Harris speaks with Jake Wood, co-founder of Team Rubicon, a group of veterans turned international first responders. Harris also talks to Skip Bennett, founder of Island Creek Oysters.
contentencoded:
Host Jessica Harris speaks with Jake Wood, co-founder of Team Rubicon, an organization of veterans turned international first responders. Harris also talks to Skip Bennett, founder of Island Creek Oysters.
